\SE[12]Haa... Haa...! \SE[52]Phew.... \SE[13]I-if I've made it
this far, then somehow...

They should have escaped this way! Pursue them! Don't let them
get away under any circumstances!!

Listen, the opponent is that Lunaroa! We cannot let her escape!
We must absolutely capture or kill her!!

\SM[nod]\SE[37]Phew.... \!\SE[3]Looks like I managed to get
through somehow.

\SE[2]But still, being told that they absolutely have to kill
me... \SE[3]They're saying such dangerous things.

\SE[12]But there was never a way out from the beginning.
\!\SM[nod]\SE[13]I have to make it through this forest and
definitely return...
